title: Bikerumor Pic Of The Day: San Diego, California
content:
Photo submitted by Zachary Blume, “Beautiful December day for a ride around San Diego California 12/5/2021.” We always love seeing photos from where you are riding and are happy to share them with our readers around the world here on the Pic Of The Day. Send in your pics with a description here.
